OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy and damp morning with
OL,6,Foutbreaks of rain, turning heavy at
OL,7,Ftimes, especially over higher ground.
OL,8,FThe rain largely dying out this
OL,9,Fafternoon, with some brighter skies
OL,10,Fdeveloping towards the north
OL,11,Fespecially. Feeling warm and humid
OL,12,Fdespite the cloud.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FRemaining cloudy across the
OL,15,Fsouth overnight with patchy drizzle,
OL,16,Fespecially over hills. Drier towards
OL,17,Fthe north with some clearer spells. A
OL,18,Fwarm night to come, especially in the
OL,19,Fsouth.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
