OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FA bright start in the north,
OL,6,Fhowever cloud further south and west
OL,7,Fwill spread northwards throughout the
OL,8,Fday. Patchy rain initially over
OL,9,Fsouthern hills, perhaps a little more
OL,10,Fwidespread later.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FBright
OL,13,Fintervals on Friday, though often
OL,14,Fcloudy with patchy rain in the north
OL,15,Fand west. Fresher on Saturday with
OL,16,Fsunshine and a few showers. Sunnier on
OL,17,FSunday, and feeling hotter.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
